WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:04.000
Create a five‑minute map before you start working.

00:04.200 --> 00:08.000
Write the desired outcome at the top of the page.

00:08.200 --> 00:12.000
List constraints: deadlines, approvals, dependencies.

00:12.200 --> 00:16.000
Note available resources and support.

00:16.200 --> 00:20.000
Circle the first next step you can do in five minutes.

00:20.200 --> 00:24.000
Schedule the next checkpoint to reassess the map.

00:24.200 --> 00:28.000
Start small, deliver a slice, then update the map.

00:28.200 --> 00:32.000
Clarity first—then execution with confidence.
